fields.headline: Prize crossword No 26,663
fields.bodyText: Special instructions: We are unable to display Maskarade’s August bank holiday puzzle online in the normal interactive format. Please use the PDF version to complete the crossword. Thematic solutions are divided into three groups (A, B and C), which are of a kind and not further defined. Solutions to the three clues marked H form an anagram of 27’s partner. The first 10 correct entries drawn win Guardian Style and Secrets of the Setters, worth £28.99. Entries to: The Guardian Crossword No 26,663, P.O. Box 6603, Birmingham, B26 3PR or Fax to 0121-742 1313 by first post on Friday 4 September. Solution and winners in the Guardian on Monday 7 September. Help Need more help? Try our frequently asked questions Technical problems and queries If you have any questions or problems of a technical nature, please send them to subshelp@guardian.co.uk Contact the crossword editor To correspond with the Quick, Quiptic, Cryptic, Prize and Genius editor email crossword.editor@guardian.co.uk
